    <system:String x:Key="BrowserAssist_Integration_WhyTheseRestrictions_Text1">VAR management is a delicate process, and with both VPM and BA managing packages by moving files around, it can lead to cache corruption in BA. This can cause errors and loaded looks or scenes to be malformed.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="BrowserAssist_Integration_WhyTheseRestrictions_Text2">To prevent breaking your scenes and forcing you to run cache rescans in VaM, VPM gracefully steps back and operates in a safe 'read-only' mode for any package managed by BA.</system:String>
